MARCFieldLabel: ACCUMULATION AND FREQUENCY OF USE NOTE (R)
MARCSubfieldLabel: Accumulation (R), Frequency of use (R), Materials specified (NR), Institution to which field applies (NR)
Justification for Mapping: This is really a note on a collection work. These notes are rare and frequency of use is out of scope for RDA. Decided it would not be worthwhile to mint items, collection entities for the sake of these notes. cey & cp 2023-12-21
Transformation Notes: Accumulation: + $a value; + Frequency of use: $b value;  + (Applies to: $3 value) + (At institution: %5 value)
